# 3102_注解补充

>![faq]+ 解析注解的技巧
>注解在哪个成分上，就拿哪个成分对象
>	比如注解作用于成员方法，就获取成员方法对应的method对象，再拿注解


### 注解解析案例 eg1
题目

![](../../../../assets/Pasted%20image%2020220930171157.png)

代码
```java
package annotationTest;  

import org.junit.Test;  

import java.lang.annotation.*;  
import java.lang.reflect.Method;  
import java.util.Arrays;  

@Target({ElementType.TYPE,ElementType.METHOD})  
@Retention(RetentionPolicy.RUNTIME)  
@interface Book {  
    String value();  
    double price() default 100;  
    String[]  author();  
}  

@Book(value = "《本草纲目》",price = 45,author = {"李时珍"})  
class BookStore{  
    @Book(value = "《龙族》",price = 65,author = {"江南","jiangnan"})  
    public void test(){  
    }  
}  

public class AnnotationTest{  
    @Test  
    public void parseClass(){  
    //    1.先得到BookStore的成分对象  
        Class c=BookStore.class;  

    //    2.判断是否存在这个注解  
        if (c.isAnnotationPresent(Book.class)){  
        //    3.获取该注解对象  
            System.out.println("类的注解解析");  
            Book book=(Book)c.getDeclaredAnnotation(Book.class);  
            System.out.println(book.value()+"\t"+book.price()+"\t"+ Arrays.toString(book.author()));  
        }  
    }  

    @Test  
    public void parseMethod() throws NoSuchMethodException {  
    //    1.得到成分  
        Method m=(BookStore.class).getDeclaredMethod("test");  
    //    判断是否存在这个注解  
        if (m.isAnnotationPresent(Book.class)){  
            System.out.println("方法的注解解析");  
            Book book=(Book) m.getDeclaredAnnotation(Book.class);  
            System.out.println(book.value()+"\t"+book.price()+"\t"+ Arrays.toString(book.author()));  
        }  
    }  
}
```

